WITH StringBench AS (
    SELECT 
        p.p_partkey,
        p.p_name,
        s.s_name AS supplier_name,
        CONCAT(p.p_name, ' - ', s.s_name) AS combined_string,
        LENGTH(CONCAT(p.p_name, ' - ', s.s_name)) AS string_length,
        SUBSTRING(p.p_comment, 1, 10) AS comment_snippet,
        REGEXP_REPLACE(p.p_comment, '[^a-zA-Z0-9]', '') AS cleaned_comment
    FROM 
        part p
    JOIN 
        partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
    JOIN 
        supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
    WHERE 
        p.p_size BETWEEN 10 AND 20
),
StringAggregates AS (
    SELECT 
        AVG(string_length) AS avg_string_length,
        MAX(string_length) AS max_string_length,
        COUNT(*) AS total_entries,
        COUNT(DISTINCT cleaned_comment) AS unique_comments
    FROM 
        StringBench
)
SELECT 
    sb.p_partkey,
    sb.p_name,
    sb.supplier_name,
    sb.combined_string,
    sb.string_length,
    sb.comment_snippet,
    sa.avg_string_length,
    sa.max_string_length,
    sa.total_entries,
    sa.unique_comments
FROM 
    StringBench sb
CROSS JOIN 
    StringAggregates sa
ORDER BY 
    sb.string_length DESC 
LIMIT 10

FROM (SELECT AVG(LENGTH(CONCAT("t0"."p_name", ' - ', "supplier"."s_name"))) AS "AVG_STRING_LENGTH", MAX(LENGTH(CONCAT("t0"."p_name", ' - ', "supplier"."s_name"))) AS "MAX_STRING_LENGTH", COUNT(*) AS "TOTAL_ENTRIES", COUNT(DISTINCT REGEXP_REPLACE("t0"."p_comment", '[^a-zA-Z0-9]', '')) AS "UNIQUE_COMMENTS"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "part"
WHERE "p_size" >= 10 AND "p_size" <= 20) AS "t0" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "t0"."p_partkey" = "s1"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "s1"."ps_suppkey") AS "t2",
(SELECT "t3"."p_partkey" AS "P_PARTKEY", "t3"."p_name" AS "P_NAME", "supplier0"."s_name" AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", CONCAT("t3"."p_name", ' - ', "supplier0"."s_name") AS "COMBINED_STRING", LENGTH(CONCAT("t3"."p_name", ' - ', "supplier0"."s_name")) AS "STRING_LENGTH", SUBSTRING("t3"."p_comment", 1, 10) AS "COMMENT_SNIPPET", REGEXP_REPLACE("t3"."p_comment", '[^a-zA-Z0-9]', '') AS "CLEANED_COMMENT"
FROM "supplier" AS "supplier0"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "part"
WHERE "p_size" >= 10 AND "p_size" <= 20) AS "t3" INNER JOIN "s1" AS "s10" ON "t3"."p_partkey" = "s10"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier0"."s_suppkey" = "s10"."ps_suppkey") AS "t4"
ORDER BY "t4"."STRING_LENGTH" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t6"
